96mmB barrels were on my bus when I bought it 20 years ago.B  One of
the skirts was cracked off and there was a hole through one piston.B 
You can draw your own conclusions, but my conclusion was that the kit
added to the heat generation of the engine and at the same time took
away from the engine's ability to reliably dissipate heat.B  Not a
good combination IMO.


-David


